{"tid":98492,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"7仔玻璃杯 做個好心入黎睇下","createTime":"2017-01-28T12:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T12:01:55.000Z","uid":75872,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d606875884790feb1bcf51feeba5b5e2f68467c","tid":98492,"uid":75872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:27:33.000Z","msg":"終於夠印花換去唯一一隻杯 <br />\n心諗初一咁普天同慶既大日子 一定可以中個布丁狗杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個7仔姐姐仲叫我宜家開 有爛就換另一隻俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知 一開⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/81Dmo22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F81Dmo22.jpg&h=58386ee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母！！！！！！<br />\n我最撚唔鍾意就係呢隻熊同佢又冇頭髮又唔著衫個個白色friend！！！！<br />\n<br />\n所以⋯⋯<br />\n有冇巴絲可以同我換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n是但一款都好 唔好係呢隻熊同個白色friend就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/202416_f4aa5591c543dc3285f2e468b743aef2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F202416_f4aa5591c543dc3285f2e468b743aef2.jpg&h=a8f5ba83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇穿冇爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a9f509d884e9e3a3b6c258e0a3b2a363a7a20b7","tid":984